From dtenenba at fredhutch.org  Fri Feb 26 05:55:09 2016
From: dtenenba at fredhutch.org (Dan Tenenbaum)
Date: Thu, 25 Feb 2016 20:55:09 -0800 (PST)
Subject: [Bioc-devel] Using non-CRAN/Bioc package
In-Reply-To: <8575_1456461983_56CFD89F_8575_8307_1_2D946D009A8A3A49B2019C6B64A972BC3B308BCD@PETREL-MA.imcb.a-star.edu.sg>
